Melissa   Claassen  Independent Director, WD-40 CompanyAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships45$105,270
Background

		Ms. Melissa Claassen serves as Vice President of Business Unit Finance for the adidas Group (XETRA: ADS) where Ms. Claassen provides financial leadership and develops collaborative teams across different company divisions. Ms. Claassen served as Chief Financial Officer of Taylor Made Golf Company, Inc. and served as its Vice President. Ms. Claassen began her career at adidas Australia in 1996 and has held many financial leadership roles throughout various regional and ... operational divisions of it including: Management Accountant, Finance Manager, Group Senior Financial Controller, Controlling Director of China, Chief Financial Officer of Adidas Hong Kong and Taiwan and Chief Financial Officer at Taylor Made-adidas Golf. Ms. Claassen has been an Independent Director of WD-40 Company since March 24, 2015.Read Full Background




