 Recommended                 "Sweet Melissa" I had never used Melissa before I recently purchased it from Plant Therapy.  I really like it.  I am prone to panic attacks, and just sniffing Melissa for a few seconds is very tranquilizing and calming.  Using Melissa has helped prevent and deal with the after affects of having panic attacks.  You do not need a lot of it  which will stretch your supply.  If you use too much Melissa or diffuse it for too long, it will withdraw maybe too much body mucous (dries your body out) and relaxes your muscles a bit too much.  Enjoy it in small doses when you need it.  It is so helpful for those with anxiety disorders like PTSD as well as for daily anxiety.  The best thing about it?  You have feelings of joy and peace, and your heart begins to sing again!  So uplifting!      Kristi On January 3, 2017
