Not all essential oils are created equal, and neither are the companies that sell them.
Whether you know nothing about essential oils and are just starting to research them or you have been using them for many, many years, we all have one thing in common: we want the purest and highest quality essential oils available.
There are many companies that sell essential oils. What makes Plant Therapy different? What makes Plant Therapy the best essential oil company?
The PEOPLE. The owners. The management team. The aromatherapist team. The customer service team. The warehouse team. And last but not least, the BEST customers. We go above and beyond just selling the highest quality essential oils. We want to do more. That is why we created the first ever full line of KidSafe® synergies. Formulated by Robert Tisserand, parents can know without a doubt that they are helping bless the lives of their children with the safest and most effective oils on the market for their young ones.

About the People







The Owners
Chris and Amanda Jones both grew up near Twin Falls, Idaho. They married in 2002 and soon after started a family that has grown into four beautiful daughters. Growing up around entrepreneurs and a mother who was a certified aromatherapist, Chris and Amanda saw the need for a different kind of essential oil company. One where you could find the highest quality essential oils at a more affordable price. They wanted to make a difference and they have!
"Our ultimate goal is not to be the largest essential oil company; it is to positively impact the lives of as many people as humanly possible. Ultimately, I feel this is possible only by providing our customers with an exceptional experience that keeps them coming back. By selling such a high quality product at an affordable price, we not only positively affect the lives of our customers, it also gives us the financial means by which we can help those who are less fortunate to live a happier, healthier, and more productive life."
-Chris Jones







The Management Team
Chris, Retha, Paul and Lori. We are just one big happy family. No, really, we are! Paul and Retha are brother and sister. Chris is our brother-in-law. Although Lori isn’t technically related, we will claim her! We don’t think there is anything better than working with family. It is said, that family run businesses "have a longer-term view of investment, they're more stable, and inspire more trust and commitment in their employees." -Business Insider
We get so much more done at our board meetings when we don’t have to beat around the bush. Decisions get made a lot quicker this way!

The Aromatherapist Team
How many companies have a full team of Aromatherapists on staff to answer any aromatherapy questions you have? Well, Plant Therapy does! Quality, education and safety are all very important to Plant Therapy, and our aromatherapist team is here to help YOU. Whether you are just starting out and know nothing about essential oils or you are well oiled, we can help! Our Aromatherapists want your essential oil experience to be the absolute best it can be by getting the most out of the oils you already have or the ones you want to have.

The Customer Service Team
You will quickly learn who they are and you will quickly learn to love them. Our customer service team is the best there is. Why? Because they truly care. They care about you. They care about your experience. They care about the quality of products you receive. They want you to have the best experience you could possibly have while learning about essential oils, searching essential oils and buying essential oils. They are always on YOUR side!

The Warehouse Team
You might not know their names like you do with our customer service team or our Aromatherapists, but this team is amazing. They work very hard to make sure when you open your highly awaited package from Plant Therapy, that your experience is the best. Plant Therapy is growing faster than we could have ever imagined and the warehouse team is always working overtime to keep up. They are the behind-the-scenes powerhouse!

The Best Customers
Some of you might be wondering why our customers are on the list of what makes Plant Therapy the best essential oil company? Let me tell you. Our customers know essential oils. And our customers hold Plant Therapy up to the highest standards. They know what to look for when buying an essential oil. They know what quality is. They know what to expect. They know what they deserve. And they know they can get it from Plant Therapy. We work hand-in-hand with our customers to always make sure we are providing the absolute highest quality essential oils. If we weren’t, our customers would let us know ;)



